          <span class="ml-cem__pillar-name">CPNP</span>
          <h3 class="ml-cem__pillar-title">Notification européenne</h3>
          <p class="ml-cem__pillar-text">Enregistrement de vos produits au portail Cosmetic Products Notification Portal, obligatoire avant la mise sur le marché.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ml-cem__pillar" data-step-n="03" data-ml-reveal>
          <div class="ml-cem__pillar-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10 2v7.5a4 4 0 0 1-1.172 2.828L3.5 17.5A3 3 0 0 0 5.621 22.5h12.758A3 3 0 0 0 20.5 17.5l-5.328-5.172A4 4 0 0 1 14 9.5V2"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="16" y2="2"/></svg></div>
          <span class="ml-cem__pillar-name">TESTS</span>
          <h3 class="ml-cem__pillar-title">Stabilité & compatibilité</h3>
